<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pesanan Berhasil</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Menggunakan ikon dan font yang sama dengan halaman utama untuk konsistensi -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bs-dark-rgb: 28, 28, 30;
            --bs-body-bg: #121212;
            --bs-body-color: #e0e0e0;
            --bs-border-color: #3a3a3c;
            --accent-color: #fca311;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bs-body-bg);
            color: var(--bs-body-color);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--accent-color);
            border-color: var(--accent-color);
            color: #121212;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #e8920a;
            border-color: #e8920a;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .text-success {
            color: #28a745 !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="text-center">
        <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success" style="font-size: 80px;"></i>
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mt-3">Pesanan Dikonfirmasi!</h1>
        <p class="lead">Jadwal Anda telah berhasil dicatat. Notifikasi (simulasi) telah dikirim ke tukang cukur.</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">Buat Pesanan Baru</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

